description: The foodies on the streets of New Jersey can delight in DeLorenzo’s famous and award-winning Trenton Tomato Pies, all thanks to this exciting truck!This mobile kitchen is where you can find your fix for the most delicious cheesy pizza, and if you’re looking for quality catering, this is the crew for you. They’re happy to work with you to custom design the perfect menu, and no matter the size of your event, these pies will come out hot and fresh. For a wonderful taste of a local favorite, you just gotta know that DeLorenzo’s is the way to go.
name: DeLorenzo's Pizza On The Go
